'''Wera Benedicta Hobhouse''' (genys '''von Reden'''; 8 Hwevrel [[1960]] yn [[Hanover]], [[Almayn|Almayn West]]) yw politegores [[Breten Veur|a Vreten]] hag an [[Chi Kemmynyon a'n Ruwvaneth Unys|Esel Senedh]]  rag [[Bath (pastell vro Senedhek RU)|Bath]] a-dhia [[Dewisyans ollgemmyn Ruwvaneth Unys, 2017|2017]]. An esel a'n [[Parti Livrel Werinel]] yw hi.

Yn derowel, Hobhouse o esel a'n [[Parti Gwithadorek]] ha konselores withadorek mes hi a wrug defectya dhe'n [[Parti Livrel Werinel]] gans hy kour yn 2005.<ref>[https://rochdalelibdems.org.uk/en/article/2005/0090526/rochdale-tories-in-meltdown-as-councillors-defect Rochdale Tories in meltdown as Councillors defect], ''Rochdale Liberal Democrats'' (yn Sowsnek), 8 March 2005, kyrgys 25 Est 2020</ref>

Hi a veu etholys y'n [[Dewisyans ollgemmyn Ruwvaneth Unys, 2017|etholans 2017]] rag Bath, ow fethas an ombrofyer gwithadorek gans 5694 votys.<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14000547#election2017-logo Bath Election 2017 Results], ''BBC'' (yn Sowsnek), kyrgys 25 Est 2020</ref> Hi a veu dasetholys yn [[Dewisyans ollgemmyn Ruwvaneth Unys, 2019|2019]] gans rann vrassa a 12,322 votys.<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14000547 Bath Parliamentary constituency LD Hold], ''BBC'' (yn Sowsnek), kyrgys 25 Est 2020</ref>

